{"id": "1471485783239299185", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "108392615644278784", "author_name": "alistiel", "author_bot": false, "content": "When you say 'take the lore 100%' what exactly do you mean?\n\nThere are a few characters who are inspired by Lovecraft's more eldritch entities, but most of them have a significant departure from their original. Off of the top of my head, I think Tulu is supposed to be Cthulu, and Thais is Shub-Niggurath", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T12:39:09.608000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471485869452951666", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "108392615644278784", "author_name": "alistiel", "author_bot": false, "content": "Reimagining Cthulu as an anime boy is liable to drive people to madness, I suppose...", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T12:39:30.163000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471485978341412884", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "108392615644278784", "author_name": "alistiel", "author_bot": false, "content": "Some of the characters are also original, I believe, but I'm not familiar with a lot of HP Lovecraft's works, so a lot of references are definitely going missed in my case", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T12:39:56.124000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
