{"id": "1471486206691774687", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "108392615644278784", "author_name": "alistiel", "author_bot": false, "content": "As for the world question, yes and no. Explaining much further involves some spoilers.", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T12:40:50.567000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471529280289636383", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 19, "author_id": "229363452026552323", "author_name": "anikid9000", "author_bot": false, "content": "Well in Morimens Tulu is not directly Cthulhu", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T15:32:00.113000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["108392615644278784"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1471485869452951666", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471529723325710389", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "229363452026552323", "author_name": "anikid9000", "author_bot": false, "content": "He's more of an adaptation of the various ancient civilization rulers who worshipped Cthulhu in Lovecraft such as the king of Atlantis and those other sunken countries, drawing a lot specifically from the background explored in The Mound", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T15:33:45.741000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471530140935655466", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 19, "author_id": "229363452026552323", "author_name": "anikid9000", "author_bot": false, "content": "There's also a lot less original characters than you would think. Nearly all of them are a nod to a Lovecraft, Derleth or some other contemporary story", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T15:35:25.307000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1471485978341412884", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471530409451065547", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "108392615644278784", "author_name": "alistiel", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm imagining a grand total of maybe one or two wholly original characters here. Not counting Mouchette. Who... hell, maybe her, too?", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T15:36:29.326000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1471531396878307581", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "229363452026552323", "author_name": "anikid9000", "author_bot": false, "content": "A decent amount of the characters are blends of so many different cross-story elements that they might as well be viewed as a 'OC' such as 24 while others weirdly adhere to the source text quite well such as everyone's favorite maid", "timestamp": "2026-02-12T15:40:24.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
